OL,3,CHow to protect yourself from rogue
OL,4,Cbuilders
OL,6,FFor many people, improving their home
OL,7,Fis a dream that they have. Whether
OL,8,Fit's adding an extra bedroom for the
OL,9,Fchildren or simply making their living
OL,10,Fspace more attractive - the thought of
OL,11,Fhome improvement is very attractive.
OL,13,FBut the costs are getting higher and
OL,14,Fhigher every year, especially with the
OL,15,Frise in the price of building
OL,16,Fmaterials. It can be one of the
OL,17,Fbiggest expenditures a household can
OL,18,Fmake - sometimes costing nearly as
OL,19,Fmuch as the house itself.
