OL,3,CHow to protect yourself from rogue
OL,4,Cbuilders
OL,6,FIf it goes well, it can add value to
OL,7,Fyour property and make a wise
OL,8,Finvestment.
OL,10,FHowever, when it goes wrong, it can
OL,11,Fleave the homeowner thousands of
OL,12,Fpounds out of pocket. It's also an
OL,13,Fextremely stressful experience and
OL,14,Fhighly emotional as it can turn the
OL,15,Fplace we call home into a living
OL,16,Fnightmare.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/12
