OL,3,CHow to protect yourself from rogue
OL,4,Cbuilders
OL,6,FTheir main tips are to make sure you
OL,7,Flook at any qualifications your
OL,8,Fpotential builder has, check jobs they
OL,9,Fhave previously done. You could even
OL,10,Fask to speak to customers who have
OL,11,Fused their services in the past. You
OL,12,Fshould also ask to check their
OL,13,Finsurance to make sure they have
OL,14,Fthings like liability insurance.
OL,16,FOften the cheapest quote isn't the
OL,17,Fbest quote - don't forget, if problems
OL,18,Fdo arise you need to feel confident
OL,19,Fthat your builder will help you to
OL,20,Fsolve them.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/12
