OL,3,CHow to protect yourself from rogue
OL,4,Cbuilders
OL,6,FIt is important to get things written
OL,7,Fdown at the beginning of the build and
OL,8,Fkeep records and photos so that if a
OL,9,Fdispute arises, you have proof.
OL,11,FOf course, you should also check
OL,12,Fwhether or not your building work
OL,13,Frequires planning permission which the
OL,14,Flocal authority will be able to advise
OL,15,Fyou on.
OL,17,FIf things do go wrong. you can speak
OL,18,Fto a dedicated Citzens Advice helpline
OL,19,Fbut they will only be able to give you
OL,20,Fgeneral advice.
