OL,3,CHow to protect yourself from rogue
OL,4,Cbuilders
OL,6,FIf you can't agree a resolution with
OL,7,Fyour builder you can contact something
OL,8,Fcalled 'alternative dispute
OL,9,Fresolution', which is a way of solving
OL,10,Fdisagreements without going to court.
OL,12,FOther than that you'd have to go to a
OL,13,Fcivil claims court to try to get the
OL,14,Fbuilder to finish or repair any
OL,15,Fdefects or to get any money back you
OL,16,Fthink you are owed.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/12
