OL,3,CHow to protect yourself from rogue
OL,4,Cbuilders
OL,6,FUnder The Consumer Rights Act 2015
OL,7,Ftraders are required to carry out a
OL,8,Fservice with reasonable care and
OL,9,Fskill, and within a reasonable time.
OL,10,FHowever, some people find that legal
OL,11,Faction is daunting and aren't always
OL,12,Fconfident it will lead to the outcomes
OL,13,Fthey want.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/12
