OL,3,CHow to protect yourself from rogue
OL,4,Cbuilders
OL,6,FTrading Standards will only intervene
OL,7,Fif they think the work is dangerous
OL,8,Fand does not comply with building
OL,9,Fregulations - things like faulty
OL,10,Felectrical wiring. They will usually
OL,11,Fonly investigate if there is criminal
OL,12,Factivity such as a builder is
OL,13,Foperating under a firm that has
OL,14,Falready gone bust or other unlawful
OL,15,Factivity.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/12
