OL,3,CHow to protect yourself from rogue
OL,4,Cbuilders
OL,6,FMany people in the building trade and
OL,7,Fsome trade organisations don't feel
OL,8,Fthat there is enough protection for
OL,9,Fcustomers. There is currently no legal
OL,10,Fregistration scheme for builders and
OL,11,Fthere is no requirement for a builder
OL,12,Fto have any form of qualifications.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/12
