OL,3,CHow to protect yourself from rogue
OL,4,Cbuilders
OL,6,FThe Federation of Master Builders is
OL,7,Fone body which wants to see compulsory
OL,8,Flicensing for small and medium sized
OL,9,Fbuilding firms. It's a scheme that
OL,10,Falready operates in countries like the
OL,11,FUS, Australia and New Zealand. Its
OL,12,Fsupporters say it would improve
OL,13,Fquality, protect consumers from
OL,14,Fincompetent contractors, and provide
OL,15,Fconsumers with redress for poor-
OL,16,Fquality work.
OL,18,FThere was a Westminster Hall debate
OL,19,Flast month (November 13th) where this
OL,20,Fsubject was discussed with MPs.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/12
