OL,3,CHow to protect yourself from rogue
OL,4,Cbuilders
OL,6,FHowever the minister for employment
OL,7,Frights and consumer protection in the
OL,8,FDepartment for Business & Trade, Kate
OL,9,FDearden, said that a licensing scheme
OL,10,Fwould add extra costs to building work
OL,11,Fand she didn't feel it would
OL,12,Fnecessarily reduce the incidence of
OL,13,Fpoor-quality work.
OL,15,FShe pointed out that there is a
OL,16,FGovernment-backed scheme called the
OL,17,FTrustMark scheme so it appears that
OL,18,Fcurrently there are no firm proposals
OL,19,For new legislation on the cards.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/12
