OL,3,CHow to protect yourself from rogue
OL,4,Cbuilders
OL,6,FThe best thing to do is to check out
OL,7,Fyour builder beforehand and try to
OL,8,Fkeep any correspondence or contracts
OL,9,Fin case anything does go wrong.
OL,11,FBut at the moment it seems many people
OL,12,Ffeel unprotected by the law and they
OL,13,Fcan be left thousands of pounds out of
OL,14,Fpocket.
